//   state-funded-firewalled   = government-funded WITH statutory editorial firewall
//   public-funded-independent = publicly funded, editorially independent by charter/statute
// NOT exhaustive (see KNOWN_LIMITATIONS.md §4). incentive_floor = min incentive-conflict applied.
